333    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.PROJECT_ID, GbifTerm.projectId);
334    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.CHECKLIST_KEY, GbifTerm.checklistKey);
335    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.GEOLOGICAL_TIME, GbifTerm.geologicalTime);
336    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.LITHOSTRATIGRAPHY, GbifTerm.lithostratigraphy);
337    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.BIOSTRATIGRAPHY, GbifTerm.biostratigraphy);
338    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.EVENT_DATE_GTE, GbifInternalTerm.eventDateGte);
339    paramMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DNA_SEQUENCE_ID, GbifTerm.dnaSequenceID);
340    eventsMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.MEASUREMENT_TYPE, DwcTerm.measurementType);
341    eventsMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.MEASUREMENT_TYPE_ID, ObisTerm.measurementTypeID);
342    // Add all from EVENTS_PARAM_TO_TERM
343    paramMap.putAll(EVENTS_PARAM_TO_TERM);
344    PARAM_TO_TERM = Collections.unmodifiableMap(paramMap);
345
346    // Build ARRAY_STRING_TERMS with LinkedHashMap to preserve insertion order
347    Map<SearchParameter, Term> arrayMap = new LinkedHashMap<>();
348    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.NETWORK_KEY, GbifInternalTerm.networkKey);
349    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DWCA_EXTENSION, GbifInternalTerm.dwcaExtension);
350    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.IDENTIFIED_BY_ID, DwcTerm.identifiedByID);
351    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.RECORDED_BY_ID, DwcTerm.recordedByID);
352    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DATASET_ID, DwcTerm.datasetID);
353    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DATASET_NAME, DwcTerm.datasetName);
354    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.OTHER_CATALOG_NUMBERS, DwcTerm.otherCatalogNumbers);
355    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.RECORDED_BY, DwcTerm.recordedBy);
356    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.IDENTIFIED_BY, DwcTerm.identifiedBy);
357    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.PREPARATIONS, DwcTerm.preparations);
358    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.SAMPLING_PROTOCOL, DwcTerm.samplingProtocol);
359    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.PROJECT_ID, GbifTerm.projectId);
360    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.GEOREFERENCED_BY, DwcTerm.georeferencedBy);
361    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.HIGHER_GEOGRAPHY, DwcTerm.higherGeography);
362    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.ASSOCIATED_SEQUENCES, DwcTerm.associatedSequences);
363    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DNA_SEQUENCE_ID, GbifTerm.dnaSequenceID);
364    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.MEASUREMENT_TYPE, DwcTerm.measurementType);
365    arrayMap.put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.MEASUREMENT_TYPE_ID, ObisTerm.measurementTypeID);
366
367    // event array params
368    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.MEASUREMENT_TYPE, DwcTerm.measurementType);
369    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.MEASUREMENT_TYPE_ID, ObisTerm.measurementTypeID);
370    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.FUNDING_ATTRIBUTION_ID, DwcTerm.fundingAttributionID);
371    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.FUNDING_ATTRIBUTION, DwcTerm.fundingAttribution);
372    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.PROJECT_TITLE, DwcTerm.projectTitle);
373    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.DATASET_ID, DwcTerm.datasetID);
374    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.DATASET_NAME, DwcTerm.datasetName);
375    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.DWCA_EXTENSION, GbifInternalTerm.dwcaExtension);
376    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.MEDIA_TYPE, GbifTerm.mediaType);
377    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.NETWORK_KEY, GbifInternalTerm.networkKey);
378    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.SAMPLING_PROTOCOL, DwcTerm.samplingProtocol);
379    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.GEOREFERENCED_BY, DwcTerm.georeferencedBy);
380    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.HIGHER_GEOGRAPHY, DwcTerm.higherGeography);
381    arrayMap.put(EventSearchParameter.PROJECT_ID, DwcTerm.projectID);
382
383    ARRAY_STRING_TERMS = Collections.unmodifiableMap(arrayMap);
384  }
385
386  private static final Map<SearchParameter, Term> DENORMED_TERMS = Collections.emptyMap();
387
388  @Override
389  public Term term(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
390    return PARAM_TO_TERM.get(searchParameter);
391  }
392
393  @Override
394  public boolean isArray(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
395    return ARRAY_STRING_TERMS.containsKey(searchParameter);
396  }
397
398  @Override
399  public Term getTermArray(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
400    return ARRAY_STRING_TERMS.get(searchParameter);
401  }
402
403  @Override
404  public boolean isDenormedTerm(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
405    return DENORMED_TERMS.containsKey(searchParameter);
406  }
407
408  @Override
409  public SearchParameter getDefaultGadmLevel() {
410    return OccurrenceSearchParameter.GADM_LEVEL_0_GID;
411  }
412
413  @Override
414  public boolean includeNullInPredicate(SimplePredicate<SearchParameter> predicate) {
415    return OccurrenceSearchParameter.DISTANCE_FROM_CENTROID_IN_METERS == predicate.getKey()
416        && (predicate instanceof GreaterThanOrEqualsPredicate
417            || predicate instanceof GreaterThanPredicate);
418  }
